                "Interact with the bot by typing in commands.\nMake sure to spell your words correctly, so that the bot understands them.\nWhen chatting with ChatBot, type \"spec\" or \"specification\" to go to SpecBot,\nwho will answer all the questions about the specification and the exams.\nWhen chatting with SpecBot, type \"quit\" to go back to chatting with ChatBot.\nWhen chatting with ChatBot, type \"quit\" to stop chatting."
